#####Important##########

TO DO CHATBOT TO YOUR PAGE YOU NEED TO COPY BELOW SCRIPTS TO YOUR INDEX.HTML INDEX.PHP FILE.


COPY THOSE SCRIPTS AT THE BEGGINING OF YOUR INDEX FILE


<script src="widget.js"></script>
<script>
    var botmanWidget = {
        frameEndpoint: 'chat.html',
        introMessage: 'Salutare! Cu ce te pot ajuta?',
        chatServer : 'botman.php', 
        title: 'Chatbot',
        headerTextColor: '#fff',
        mainColor: '#60645f',
        bubbleAvatarUrl: 'https://www.applozic.com/assets/resources/images/Chat-Bot-Icon@512px.svg',
        aboutLink: null,
        aboutText: null,
        placeholderText: 'Trimite un mesaj...'
    }; 
</script>